                "imgDesc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Sorush</span> can use her power to <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">awaken the Residual Pari inside the Fravashi Trees</span>. If the languishing obsessions of these spirits are extinguished, perhaps these Pari, thus scattered abroad, may yet meet again in the sea of flowers...</p><p>Offer the Plumes of Purifying Light you obtain from Fravashi Trees to the Amrita Pool and return all the memories of Khvarena back to the flowery sea!</p>",
